Package com.simukappu.coherence.writequeue

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClearWriteQueueProcessor
    EntryProcessor class to clear write behind queue of read/write backing map scheme cache.
    This processor should be invoked from invokeAll method since process method should run only one time for each node.

    For example, invoke as follows:
    NamedCache<Object, Object> namedCache = CacheFactory.getCache("CacheName"); Map<Object, Map.Entry<Integer, Integer>> mapResults = namedCache.invokeAll(new AlwaysFilter<Object>(), new ClearWriteQueueProcessor(targetCacheName));
    GetWriteQueueSizeProcessor
    EntryProcessor class to get the size of write behind queue in read/write backing map scheme cache.
    This processor should be invoked from invokeAll method since process method should run only one time for each node.

    For example, invoke as follows:
    NamedCache<Object, Object> namedCache = CacheFactory.getCache("CacheName"); Map<Object, Map.Entry<Integer, Integer>> mapResults = namedCache.invokeAll(new AlwaysFilter<Object>(), new GetWriteQueueSizeProcessor(targetCacheName));
